    "description": "# 📘 SWIPE SLANG API – Overview\n\nThe **SWIPE LANG API** is a scalable and secure backend system built for a modern **slang learning application with an integrated LMS (Learning Management System)**. It supports structured learning content such as courses, lessons, and modules, along with slang word learning features, user progress tracking, subscription management, and a complete authentication system.\n\nThe system is designed to deliver smooth, secure, and structured user experiences for learners and administrators.\n\nBuilt with a clean RESTful architecture, **JWT-based authentication**, strong request validation, role-based access control (RBAC), and payment integration, SWIPE LANG is production-ready and designed for scalability, security, and maintainability.\n\n---\n\n# 🌐 Base URL Configuration\n\nThe API uses environment variables for flexible deployment across production and local environments.\n\n### 🔹 Environment Variables\n\n```\n{{domain}}  = https://abcnerd-backend.onrender.com{{domain}}  = http://localhost:5000{{baseapi}} = /api/v1\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# 🔹 Full Endpoint Format\n\n```\n{{domain}}{{baseapi}}/{resource}/{endpoint}\n\n ```\n\n---\n\n# 🔹 Example Endpoints\n\nProduction:\n\n```\nhttps://abcnerd-backend.onrender.com/api/v1/auth/login\n\n ```\n\nLocal Development:\n\n```\nhttp://localhost:5000/api/v1/auth/login\n\n ```",
